{"tid":792480,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【安泰邪邨】男子疑自天橋飛墮　跌落山坡渠邊喪生","createTime":"2018-08-24T14:53:19.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-25T02:01:58.000Z","uid":50162,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"0f8bdda793aefcb1958d2ca072e6d20ef1a70b94","tid":792480,"uid":50162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T14:53:19.000Z","msg":"秀茂坪男子倒斃山邊，警封鎖調查。早上7時許，有晨運人士行經安泰邨連接順安邨約12層高升降機行人天橋時，發現有人倒臥在山坡渠邊，大聲呼叫對方無反應，隨即報警求助。警方聯同消防人員趕至，由消防員游繩而下，經檢驗後證實男子已明顯死亡。警方封鎖現場調查，初步懷疑死者由高處墮下死亡，正調查其身份及死因。<br />\n<br />\n現場消息，死者年約60歲，穿白色上衣、灰色褲及黑布鞋，身上沒有身份證明文件。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n防止自殺求助熱線：<br />\n香港撒瑪利亞防止自殺會： 2389 2222<br />\n生命熱線： 2382 0000<br />\n明愛向晴軒： 18288<br />\n社會福利署： 2343 2255<br />\n撒瑪利亞會熱線(多種語言)： 2896 0000<br />\n東華三院芷若園： 18281<br />\n醫管局精神健康專線： 2466 7350<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170830/photo/bkn-20170830081712073-0830_00822_001_01b.jpg?20170830113643\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170830%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170830081712073-0830_00822_001_01b.jpg%3F20170830113643&h=a32ed437&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n警方在現場調查，消防準備游繩而下。(黃子喬攝)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170830/photo/bkn-20170830081712073-0830_00822_001_02b.jpg?20170830113643\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170830%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170830081712073-0830_00822_001_02b.jpg%3F20170830113643&h=fb307d1f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n男子由行人天橋躍下身亡。(黃子喬攝)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170830/photo/bkn-20170830081712073-0830_00822_001_03b.jpg?20170830113643\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170830%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170830081712073-0830_00822_001_03b.jpg%3F20170830113643&h=7a151838&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n男子倒斃安泰邨山坡渠邊，消防到場拯救。(黃子喬攝)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170830/photo/bkn-20170830081712073-0830_00822_001_04b.jpg?20170830113643\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170830%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170830081712073-0830_00822_001_04b.jpg%3F20170830113643&h=4b0d2f4f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n警員在山邊調查。(黃子喬攝)<br />\n<br />\n新聞來源：<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170830/bkn-20170830081712073-0830_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170830%2Fbkn-20170830081712073-0830_00822_001.html&d=sF0Pb0B18CkJn4xbHXEfCdtKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=6bec9e49\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170830/bkn-20170830081712073-0830_00822_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n＃安泰邪邨 ＃前石礦場 ＃死亡勝地 ＃賤人賤邨"},{"pid":"9d8fce1b22cff6d4e79c6296fd37ed324fe3bfb8","tid":792480,"uid":44454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T14:59:21.000Z","msg":"掃墓坪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be378151d71099b15f0b2498c04159ffabd950b7","tid":792480,"uid":186323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T15:02:45.000Z","msg":"又搵替死鬼"},{"pid":"210f9f54356e092816eea7daba555ede071892d9","tid":792480,"uid":14337,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T15:03:12.000Z","msg":"民排安泰好似發生好多事咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"989aff82fa72a48ee450dedcdc5f004b7f62defc","tid":792480,"uid":14337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"210f9f54356e092816eea7daba555ede071892d9","tid":792480,"uid":14337,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T15:03:12.000Z","msg":"民排安泰好似發生好多事咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T15:03:30.000Z","msg":"呢排"},{"pid":"a743f4fead4a4ef434ef18b25b82ba22c7d1d862","tid":792480,"uid":71748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T15:12:39.000Z","msg":"安泰同寶達果面好高好恐怖<img src=\"/assets/face